### Orders Controller Tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@adminToken = PUT_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE
@customerToken = PUT_CUSTOMER_TOKEN_HERE
@orderId = PUT_ORDER_ID_HERE


### ─── الطلبات (عميل) ────────────────────────────────────

### Create Order from Cart (إنشاء طلب من السلة)
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Accept-Language: ar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "shippingAddress": {
    "street": "شارع الملك فهد",
    "city": "الرياض",
    "country": "السعودية",
    "zipCode": "12345"
  }
}


### Get My Orders (قائمة طلباتي)
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Accept-Language: ar


### Get My Orders Filtered by Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders?status=PENDING&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Accept-Language: ar


### Get My Order Detail (تفاصيل طلب)
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/{{orderId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Accept-Language: ar


### ─── لوحة الأدمن ────────────────────────────────────────

### Admin: Get All Orders (كل الطلبات)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar


### Admin: Filter by Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/orders?status=PENDING&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar


### Admin: Search by Order Number
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/orders?orderNumber=ORD-2026
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar


### Admin: Filter by Date Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/orders?dateFrom=2026-01-01&dateTo=2026-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar


### Admin: Update Order Status → CONFIRMED
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/orders/{{orderId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "CONFIRMED",
  "note": "تم تأكيد الطلب"
}


### Admin: Update Order Status → CANCELLED
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/orders/{{orderId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "CANCELLED",
  "note": "تم إلغاء الطلب لعدم توفر المخزون"
}


### ─── أخطاء ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### Empty Cart (سلة فارغة)
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Accept-Language: en
Content-Type: application/json

{}


### Missing Shipping Address for Physical Product
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Accept-Language: en
Content-Type: application/json

{}


### Invalid Status Transition (نقل حالة غير صالح)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/orders/{{orderId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: en
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "DELIVERED"
}


### Invalid Status Value
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/orders/{{orderId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: en
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "INVALID"
}


### Unauthorized (بدون توكن)
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders
Accept-Language: ar


### Customer Accessing Admin Route (ممنوع)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Accept-Language: ar
